{"tid":1459140,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"與其塞鐵倒不如卡閘比人免費過","createTime":"2019-08-12T16:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T19:20:13.000Z","uid":263945,"like":69,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"453a3428e37c8b91724a36c56a7dc3830e04009a","tid":1459140,"uid":263945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:14:44.000Z","msg":"P牌唔好屌我住，睇埋先屌<br />\n<br />\n好多人係出面討論緊聽日塞唔塞鐵，兄弟各自爬山我唔會反對你搞狗鐵，但係搞還搞，不如唔好塞，反而比人<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">免費搭？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你諗下，塞鐵又會比人屌又盛，相反你比人免費過又係一個經濟攻擊既手段（狗鐵大股東係政府）。要知道香港人真係好鐘意番工....但香港人亦好鐘意攞著數。你比佢免費過佢會唔過？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />分分鐘係狗鐵年年加價既情況下啲市民會多謝你都黎唔切。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n所以，與其塞鐵，不如卡閘比人免費過啦</span></span>。"},{"pid":"72c4e07a96959f68a0ffee1a772e8975a47334a5","tid":1459140,"uid":263945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:16:18.000Z","msg":"10連自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0668e7829e8b374eb409ffe1d792309adfc5431","tid":1459140,"uid":263945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:16:28.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"9962bddfa0f0e22d1b8754c5160fcea3cebedce7","tid":1459140,"uid":263945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:16:38.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"f75f7cad2794394a0851f5f7ca56a1614c655225","tid":1459140,"uid":263945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:16:48.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"04fce5efb2dd753c995163857147b61f712d4394","tid":1459140,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:16:54.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"00ffe949495cf34ad0ec941d400ec2f64414bc12","tid":1459140,"uid":263945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"63a5b2be7780204533d68f70ad4bdcb6a32e9047","tid":1459140,"uid":263945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:17:10.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"49f721d814384a67dc25957e0df294c2f16f583c","tid":1459140,"uid":263945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:17:21.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"1d591c2b5c3239d424da7faa5e74382c42e2a258","tid":1459140,"uid":263945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:17:31.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"08cffd3a37eebf3cce94c25babe4c14aade6bddd","tid":1459140,"uid":80972,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:17:32.000Z","msg":"同意!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地唔應該要塞鐵，令大家返唔到工，令佢地都嬲示威者。我地係要民意，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">令更多人企係我地呢邊!</span></span><br />\n令更多人逐步對政權反抗!<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地只要更多人一齊以小步伐，參與反政權運動，佢地就會愈來愈支持!</span></span><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n比如<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">1)令全民免費搭港鐵，免費過隧道!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2) 帶親友去連儂場，甚或去示威<br />\n<br />\n總之用佢可接受嘅方法一步一步參與運動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原理係咁<br />\nNetflix 有套Derren Brown: Pushed to the Edge，設計令普通人去殺人就係<span style=\"color: orange;\">首先令佢做d好簡單嘅野，等佢個錯愈來愈多</span>，最後就會聽話去殺人。我地唔係去殺人，但要好多和非再支持我地，就要令佢地更覺得犯法係無野，政權係可以反對!"},{"pid":"91282628b003e84bb51f855f0294c4750b6549c6","tid":1459140,"uid":263945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:17:41.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"bfcd521ab7c5f482331900996ed116fb40b3f7c2","tid":1459140,"uid":138407,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:17:45.000Z","msg":"每個站都要有人係度 點樣整壞佢個閘機呢🌚🌚"},{"pid":"b2337607e5392f15612f2af02bd29c1c278f0e10","tid":1459140,"uid":263945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T16:17:52.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"8bf410fd3a3329dcea22d34b42502